OL,3,CMan admits burning Koran
OL,5,FA man has admitted to setting fire to
OL,6,Fthe Islamic holy book the Koran which
OL,7,Fwas live-streamed on social media.
OL,9,FMartin Frost, 47 was filmed holding a
OL,10,Fflag of Israel before tearing out
OL,11,Fpages of the text and setting fire to
OL,12,Fit in Manchester on Saturday 1
OL,13,FFebruary,
OL,15,FManchester Magistrates Court heard how
OL,16,FFrost had publicised the event online
OL,17,Fbeforehand, and that it was streamed
OL,18,Fon social media.
