OL,3,CMan admits burning Koran
OL,5,FThe "trigger" for his actions was the
OL,6,Fdeath of his daughter in the Israeli
OL,7,Fconflict which had affected his mental
OL,8,Fhealth, the court heard.
OL,10,FFrost, of Stretford, Greater
OL,11,FManchester, pleaded guilty to a single
OL,12,Fcharge of racially or religiously
OL,13,Faggravated intentional harassment or
OL,14,Falarm to Fahad Iqbal, by displaying
OL,15,Fsome writing, sign or other visible
OL,16,Frepresentation which was threatening,
OL,17,Fabusive or insulting thereby causing
OL,18,Fthat or another person harassment,
OL,19,Falarm or distress.
