OL,3,CMan admits burning Koran
OL,5,FFootage of the incident from X showed
OL,6,Fthe book being burned and Frost being
OL,7,Farrested by police near to The Glade
OL,8,Fof Light, the memorial to the 22
OL,9,Fpeople killed in the Manchester Arena
OL,10,Fbombing in 2017.
OL,12,FPrior to his arrest, Frost threw the
OL,13,Fbook in the river.
OL,15,FRobin Lynch, prosecuting, told the
OL,16,Fcourt a crowd of supporters gathered
OL,17,Fnear the Glade of Light memorial when
OL,18,FFrost began tearing out pages of the
OL,19,FKoran.
