OL,3,CMan admits burning Koran
OL,5,FMr Lynch said a passer-by attempted to
OL,6,Fintervene.
OL,8,FThe prosecutor continued: "Then he
OL,9,F(Frost) ripped out pages... and sets
OL,10,Fthat page alight."
OL,12,FThe defendant told officers he was
OL,13,Fdemonstrating solidarity with another
OL,14,Fanti-Islam activist in Sweden, who was
OL,15,Frecently murdered after burning a
OL,16,FKoran.
