OL,3,CMan admits burning Koran
OL,5,FA victim impact statement from the
OL,6,Fperson who tried to intervene, said:
OL,7,F"I was quite shocked, disgusted and
OL,8,Foffended. I'm a Muslim. I still can't
OL,9,Fbelieve someone would do this.
OL,11,F"When he began to burn the Koran my
OL,12,Fheart was about to break out. This is
OL,13,Fthe most emotion I have ever felt."
OL,15,FZoe Earle, defending Frost ` who was
OL,16,Fin tears stood in the dock, said:
OL,17,F"He's extremely distressed at the
OL,18,Fdistress he's caused others as a
OL,19,Fresult of this. He needs some further
OL,20,Fhelp and support.
