OL,3,CMan admits burning Koran
OL,5,F"What triggered what happened recently
OL,6,Fis that his daughter was killed in the
OL,7,FIsraeli conflict. Her death has had a
OL,8,Fsignificant impact on his mental
OL,9,Fhealth.
OL,11,F"His mental health is clearly
OL,12,Fdeclining over the last six months."
OL,14,FThe court heard Frost has 20 previous
OL,15,Fconvictions for 47 offences, but
OL,16,Fnothing of a similar nature to the
OL,17,Fpublic order offence on Saturday.
OL,19,FJudge Margaret McCormack asked for a
OL,20,Fpre-sentence report before passing
OL,21,Fsentence.
