OL,5,FShe told Frost she was sorry for the
OL,6,Floss of his daughter, but added: "The
OL,7,FKoran is a sacred book to Muslims and
OL,8,Ftreating it as you did is going to
OL,9,Fcause extreme distress.
OL,11,F"This is a tolerant country, but we
OL,12,Fjust do not tolerate this behaviour."
OL,14,FShe bailed Frost on condition he does
OL,15,Fnot post anything further on social
OL,16,Fmedia. He will be sentenced on April
OL,17,F29.
