OL,3,CMan admits burning Koran
OL,5,FFollowing the incident, Assistant
OL,6,FChief Constable Stephanie Parker of
OL,7,FGreater Manchester Police (GMP) said:
OL,8,F"We understand the deep concern this
OL,9,Fwill cause within some of our diverse
OL,10,Fcommunities and are aware of a live
OL,11,Fvideo circulating.
OL,13,F"We made a swift arrest at the time
OL,14,Fand recognise the right people have
OL,15,Ffor freedom of expression, but when
OL,16,Fthis crosses into intimidation to
OL,17,Fcause harm or distress we will always
OL,18,Flook to take action when it is
OL,19,Freported to us."
